---
title: Lemon Tortelloni Palermo with Roasted Bell Pepper & Parmesan
description: Tender tortelloni are pretty much great in any form, but they’re *especially* great when packed with pillowy ricotta cheese. Add tender roasted bell pepper slices and a squeeze of bright, tangy lemon juice to the mix and you’ve got yourself a pasta night for the books. This divine dish is taken to the next level with a creamy, Parmesan-spiked sauce and a sprinkle of scallion greens. Be still, our pasta-loving hearts...
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/61f17a5ac1da0139b465046d-c9a78bae.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/lemon-tortelloni-palermo-61f17a5ac1da0139b465046d-bf499b0b.pdf
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/lemon-tortelloni-palermo-61f17a5ac1da0139b465046d
time required: 30 minutes
cuisine: Italian
servings: 2
nutrition:
  calories: 680 kcal
  fat: 40 g
  saturated fat: 22 g
  carbohydrates: 66 g
  sugar: 15 g
  protein: 22 g
  fiber: 8 g
  sodium: 1140 mg
author: Michelle Doll Olson
